reviewText: This is a beautiful indie movie based on the amazingly creative Sally Tomato project.  Toy Room is a fairly simple concept explored to profound levels. Toy Room the rock opera operates on many levels --  as excellent rock music, as a dramatic stage play, as a mixed media film, as a triumphant musical.  It is a complete success on its own terms. Take a chance on Toy Room; it invites you, playfully.
